{"title": "Thought Bubble Speech", "content": "Animals can't talk, but they can think, so lines that look like dialog appear in thought bubbles. Sometimes animals can communicate with each other and reply to each other's thought balloons. This means that either the thought balloons are effectively translations of Animal Talk, or all animals are telepathic.\n\nRelated to Speech-Impaired Animal, Nearly Normal Animal and Animal Talk.\n\nThis is a comic trope \u2014 the film equivalent would be to sub-title an animal.", "url": "https://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ThoughtBubbleSpeech", "media_links": ["/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Franchise/ScoobyDoo", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Franchise/Tintin", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Webcomic/TwoLumps", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Webcomic/Kurami", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Webcomic/AmazingSuperpowers", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Webcomic/LeifAndThorn", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/TheLoudHouse"], "non_media_links": ["/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/InnerMonologueConversation", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/AnimalTalk", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/SpeechImpairedAnimal", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/NearlyNormalAnimal", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/AnimalTalk", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicStrip/Peanuts", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicStrip/Garfield", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/TheSpeechless", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicStrip/FootrotFlats", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicStrip/BabyBlues", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicStrip/ThePerishers", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicStrip/Marvin", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicStrip/MotherGooseAndGrimm", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/SpeechBubbles", "http://www.twolumps.net/d/20050516.html", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ThoughtCaption", "http://www.amazingsuperpowers.com/2011/10/return-of-the-fish-2/", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/WordOfGod", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/RuleOfFunny"]}